{"id":1720692,"retrievedAt":"2026-06-25T13:39:05.278Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/wAa456bgahbsLtC0xO9OsmybvmH.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":10749,"name":"Romance"}],"homepage":"https://www.freshwave.hk/?a=doc&id=2105","id":1720692,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["HK"],"original_language":"cn","original_title":"夜來春","overview":"There are only three important things in life for saxophone player Kelvin: music, his mother and his best friend. At sixty, his life suddenly loses meaning after his mother and best friend pass away one after the other. Once a self-proclaimed loner, he now finds the solitude unbearable and worrisome. Things change when a newly divorced lounge singer Qiling starts working in the same bar. Kelvin’s heart is reignited knowing Qiling shares the same passion for oldies. When love comes knocking at the door, Kelvin finds himself ready to play an evening song.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/rDkYwWmqeO7McT2y1Iwd0fTzfVP.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":61392,"logo_path":"/e1g54NyBA3ICLice0kKOYHMc84u.png","name":"Fresh Wave","origin_country":"HK"},{"id":61393,"logo_path":"/zBPeWCDSwQ2PDSRHacdt4HPHw3n.png","name":"Hong Kong Arts Development Council","origin_country":"HK"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"HK","name":"Hong Kong"}],"release_date":"2020-06-08","revenue":0,"runtime":22,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Cantonese","iso_639_1":"cn","name":"广州话 / 廣州話"},{"english_name":"Mandarin","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"The Evening Song","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2355365,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Fonnie Ng","original_name":"吳鳳鳴","popularity":0.1935,"profile_path":"/9WwiyKAE8Qa4DutijYMpvu298zo.jpg","cast_id":6,"character":"","credit_id":"6a3cc5dcbf8e1794ca823ab3","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2322091,"known_f